00:12:50.530 --> 00:12:51.790
This is who you are.

00:12:51.790 --> 00:12:55.600
So I've had tremendous
support in learning

00:12:55.600 --> 00:13:01.000
what it is to be in love
with what God made me.

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:06.040
For instance, when I realize
and my deepest feelings were

00:13:06.040 --> 00:13:09.175
for my friends and yet we had--

