00:24:08.120 --> 00:24:09.400
and to who we are.

00:24:09.400 --> 00:24:14.280
Because so much around us
said, no, you can't be.

00:24:14.280 --> 00:24:16.090
And we said, yes, we can.

00:24:16.090 --> 00:24:18.880
Yes we can, because of God.

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:25.850
That makes people cranky, you
know, but it's true, it's true.

00:24:25.850 --> 00:24:26.560
Isn't it?

00:24:26.560 --> 00:24:27.790
ANNANDA BARCLAY: It is.

00:24:27.790 --> 00:24:31.552
So I think we take questions
now, or where are we at?

00:24:31.552 --> 00:24:33.010
SPEAKER 1: It seems
