00:24:49.570 --> 00:24:52.000
again, we've done so much
on this and the bible.

00:24:52.000 --> 00:24:55.600
And when you do this, you
think surely people see this,

00:24:55.600 --> 00:24:59.770
and hear this, it's very clear.

00:24:59.770 --> 00:25:00.730
It's not.

00:25:00.730 --> 00:25:04.900
And so what we have found in
